high_descs: Move to the large wooden dining table facing the remote on top of the table
Pick up the remote sitting on the edge of the dining table
Carry the remote control to the floor lamp sitting to the right of the window
anns.task_desc: Carry a remote while turning on the lamp

high_descs: Go right and then turn to face the table in front of the remote.
Pick the remote up from the table.
Turn around and cross the room to the right to stand in front of the lamp with a green shade.
anns.task_desc: Turn a lamp on with a remote in hand.

high_descs: Turn and move to stand at the kitchen table on the side with the remote control by a chair.
Pick up the remote control from the table.
Turn and walk around the back of the sofa and past the fireplace on the left, and then turn right and continue to the lamp in the corner.
Turn the lamp on while still holding the remote control.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote control under a lamp.
